<div class="container text-start site-section main-section">
    <h1 class="text-start">Sell To Us</h1>

    <div class="row row-cols-3 mb-4">
        <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-4 we-buy-holder">
            <div class="we-buy">
                <h2>Rare Coins</h2>
                <p>We make the strongest offers on rare coin collections in Central PA. Our deep knowledge of the market means you get a fair, expert appraisal — not a lowball offer.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-4 we-buy-holder">
            <div class="we-buy">
                <h2>Gold & Silver</h2>
                <p>Selling gold or silver bars and coins? We test for purity on the spot and make competitive cash offers. We buy everything from American Eagles to vintage poured silver bars.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-4 we-buy-holder">
            <div class="we-buy">
                <h2>Quick & Easy</h2>
                <p>No lengthy process. Tell us what you have, and we'll give you an estimate — sometimes right over the phone. We pay quickly in the format that suits you best.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sell-form-wrapper">
        <div class="sell-form-overlay">
            <h2 style="color:#1d3961; font-family:'Noto Serif Display'; font-weight:800; margin-bottom:8px;">Tell Us About Your Collection</h2>
            <p style="color:#444; margin-bottom:24px;">Fill out the form below and Tony will get back to you promptly. Include as much detail as you can about each coin — grading service, grade, year, and any special attributes help us give you the most accurate offer.</p>

            <form action="https://formspree.io/f/xpqorvdg" method="POST">
                <div class="row g-3">
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                        <label class="sell-label">Your Name</label>
                        <input class="form-control sell-input" type="text" name="name" placeholder="John Smith" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                        <label class="sell-label">Your Email</label>
                        <input class="form-control sell-input" type="email" name="email" placeholder="john@email.com" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                        <label class="sell-label">Phone Number (optional)</label>
                        <input class="form-control sell-input" type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="(717) 555-1234">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                        <label class="sell-label">Best Time to Reach You</label>
                        <input class="form-control sell-input" type="text" name="best_time" placeholder="e.g. Weekday mornings">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <label class="sell-label">Coin & Collection Details</label>
                        <textarea class="form-control sell-input" name="message" rows="10" placeholder="Please describe what you have. For each coin, include:
- Year, denomination, and mint mark (e.g. 1881-S $1 Morgan Dollar)
- Grading service and grade (e.g. PCGS MS64, NGC AU58)
- Certification number if available
- Any special attributes (CAC sticker, toning, varieties)
- Approximate quantity if selling a large collection

The more detail you provide, the faster we can get you an offer!" required></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <input type="checkbox" name="privacypolicy" id="privacypolicy" required>
                        <label for="privacypolicy" style="margin-left:8px; font-family:'Roboto'; font-size:14px;">I agree to the <a href="/privacypolicy/" target="_blank">privacy policy</a>.</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit" style="font-size:18px; padding:12px 30px;">Send Inquiry</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<script>
            (function() {
                var form = document.querySelector('.sell-form-overlay form');
                if (form) {
                    form.addEventListener('submit', function() {
                        var email = form.querySelector('input[name="email"]').value;
                        var input = document.createElement('input');
                        input.type = 'hidden';
                        input.name = '_replyto';
                        input.value = email;
                        form.appendChild(input);
                    });
                }
            })();
            </script>